        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"Miss Milner, you shall not leave the house this evening.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"I command you to stay at home this evening.\" And he walked immediately out of the apartment by another door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"What could be worse, Madam?\" cried Miss Milner; \"am not I disappointed of the ball?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"It is not the first time, I believe, you have acted contrary to that, Miss Milner,\" replied mrs Horton, and affected a tenderness of voice, to soften the harshness of her words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "Dorriforth read on, and seemed afraid of looking up, lest he should see what he could not have pardoned.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "After a few minutes' pause, and some little embarrassment on the part of mrs Horton, at the disappointment she had to encounter from this unexpected dutiful conduct, she asked Miss Milner, \"if she would now have any tea?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_23268_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/23268/3536_23268_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "She was going to reply, but found she could not, without accompanying her words with tears, therefore, after the first attempt, she desisted.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000002_000000",
