        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "mr",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "With Hugh Stanbury, Trevelyan had had a direct quarrel.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000005_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000005_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "But now, when a demand was made upon Bozzle to violate the sanctity of the clergyman's house, and withdraw the child by force or stratagem, she began to perceive that the palmy days of the Trevelyan affair were over for them, and that it would be wise on her husband's part gradually to back out of the gentleman's employment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"Gammon, Bozzle.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "We'd all be shewed up in the papers as that black, that they'd hoot us along the streets.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "It ain't the regular line of business, Bozzle; and there ain't no good to be got, never, by going off the regular line.\" Whereupon Bozzle scratched his head and again read the letter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"It ain't to be done, you know,\" said Bozzle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"Of course it ain't,\" said mrs Bozzle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"It ain't to be done anyways;--not in my way of business.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "The paternal parent has a right to his infants, no doubt.\" That was Bozzle's law.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"I don't believe it, b\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"But he have, I tell you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "I don't believe a bit of his rights.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "He'll get the child fast enough if he'll go before the court.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"I'll tell you what it is, b,\" exclaimed mrs Bozzle, \"it's my belief as he ain't quite right up here;\" and mrs Bozzle touched her forehead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"It's love for her as has done it then,\" said Bozzle, shaking his head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"I'm not a taking of her part, b A woman as has a husband as finds her with her wittels regular, and with what's decent and comfortable beside, ought to be contented.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "Drat 'em all; what is it they wants?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "They don't know what they wants.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "But as for this here child, b--.\" At that moment there came a knock at the door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "mrs Bozzle going into the passage, opened it herself, and saw a strange gentleman.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000020_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000020_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "Bozzle, who had stood at the inner door, saw that the gentleman was mr Trevelyan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "Then Bozzle came forward and introduced his wife.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000021_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000021_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "mrs Bozzle had set a chair for him, but he had declined to sit down.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000021_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000021_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "\"Perhaps you could put on your coat, and walk out with me for a few minutes,\" said Trevelyan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000021_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000021_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "mrs Bozzle, who well understood that business was business, and that wives were not business, felt no anger at this, and handed her husband his best coat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3536_8226_000021_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3536/8226/3536_8226_000021_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3536",
        "content": "The well brushed hat was fetched from a cupboard, and it was astonishing to see how easily and how quickly the outer respectability of Bozzle was restored.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
